latestIgtvVideos.title: Green tea scrub☘️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey my lovelies💕

I would be sharing with you my go to mask these days which is so easy and yet so effective at the same time🤩

For this you need to have a pack of green tea, honey, pinch of baking soda and few drops of  fresh lemon juice💁🏻‍♀️

All you need to do is mix all these ingredients well with a spoon and apply it on your clean face. Leave it on for good 20 minutes and then massage it gently in your skin as your scrub your face and wash off with plain water & that’s all😍😍

This mask rich in anti oxidants would leave your skin so smooth and supple and brings you back all the moisture and hydration needed🌸

⚠️ Always do patch test before applying on your face!

latestIgtvVideos.title: DIY coffee pack for instant glow🤎
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey lovelies💓
.
I have come up with an amazing face mask for dewy glowy skin like never before and its simple and with the ingredients available in your kitchen🤩
.
For this DIY you need: 
🤎1 teaspoon coffee
🤎 1 teaspoon sugar 
🤎 1 teaspoon lemon juice
.
Pour the ingredients in a bowl and mix it well
Apply it on your cleansed  face with the help or brush or your fingers. Keep it for good 20 minutes and then rinse it off with water💫
And here you go , you are left with amazing glowy smooth skin instantly.
.
🦋Important- Always do a patch test before applying on your face🙌🏻
.
🌈Coffee face pack benefits🌈
.
🤎Coffee n sugar being natural exfoliants helps in removing dull skin.
.
🤎Also it helps in reducing the tan on the skin
.
🤎It provides the moisturisation and nourishment needed for skin
.
🤎It has anti ageing properties , and also cures acne scars
.
.
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:

you need to take 1-2 spoons of yoghurt or curd, 1 spoon honey and half squeezed lemon. Then mix it all together stir it well and make a paste like consistency!
